snippet.title: Temple of the Lizard Men 5 - Release Trailer!
snippet.description:
Ladies and gentlemen, I am proud to announce the release of Temple of the Lizard Men 5! I will provide a link  below to download it. As of right now, you can download it from DropBox. Get ready for an adventure YOU get to create!
Enjoy!

Temple of the Lizard Men 5 - GOLD EDITION AVAILABLE!:
https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/xvh7bpuv97at9udw6xuf3/lmtmpl5_Gold.zip?rlkey=5t4b0zly921br36a71bbq9uxs&dl=0

MUSIC CREDIT:
Nightwish - Tribal
